Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO_1 As String
INSTRUMENTO_1 = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") PONTEIRO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO_1 = "_" Then ' Para todos os intrumentos (exceto PDITs) & "A"
ALM_1_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 2, 10) ALM_1_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 6, 8) NUMERO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 5, 8) End If
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '" & NUMERO_1 & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1_2 & "')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & NUMERO_1 & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1_2 & "%')"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO_1 As String
INSTRUMENTO_1 = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") PONTEIRO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO_1 = "_" Then ' Para todos os intrumentos (exceto PDITs) & "A"
ALM_1_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 2, 10) ALM_1_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 6, 8) NUMERO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO_1, 5, 8) End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '" & NUMERO_1 & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1_2 & "')" ' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & NUMERO_1 & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1_2 & "%')"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_SP_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F1}" End If
End Sub Private Sub NumericInput_CV_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F2}" End If
End Sub
